{"tid":1799653,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[抗爭生活化] #NewYearsResolution，將你2020大計寫出黎，令黃色生活成為潮流。","createTime":"2019-12-27T06:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T17:35:48.000Z","uid":14583,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fbbd6243b376d3719aa34d82832f7c1cb6f80f9f","tid":1799653,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:16:31.000Z","msg":"每年大家指定都要打卡<strong>&quot;<span style=\"font-size: large;\">What is your New Years Resolution for 2020</span>&quot;</strong>，今年香港人作為全球觸目既一群人，當然要諗計壯大黃色經濟圈，將佢生活化，國際化我，同時將抗爭生活化，建設民主香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係拋磚引玉既New Years Resolution，輕輕分左兩個level，強烈歡迎大家討論：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><em>中產以下，30歲以下</em></strong></span><br />\n1. 減少答黨鐵，將巴士融入生活，每月抽兩個星期完全唔答黨鐵 <span style=\"color: teal;\">#boycottMTR</span><br />\n2. 減少30% 非必要開支，留作儲蓄，以備長期抗爭 <br />\n3. 積極尋求受影響既黃色商店，做到破壞經濟之餘，令黃店逆市回升<br />\n4. 主動協助身邊前線朋友，多食飯，多請客<br />\n5. TVB劇集？不了。大陸劇？不了。進化睇歐美劇！擴闊視野同時學好英文，仲可以收TVB皮 <span style=\"color: teal;\">#boycottTVB</span><br />\n6. 做一樣幫助香港邁向民主既事，例如：加入工會，定期討論；加入社區成為區議員義工；減少幫襯協助籠斷市場既餐廳；參加公民課堂<br />\n7. 身壯力健，全民練體能<br />\n8. 抗爭進化，為自己定立長期目標，唔會越過底線，但唔會固步自封，謹守崗位。<br />\n9. 裝備自己，成為對社會影嚮力既人，發展一項全新既技能，嘗試張之應用係抗爭，例如：學外語，做好國外文宣，同時有利就業前景<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><em>中產或以上，30戱以上</em></strong></span><br />\n1. 將儲蓄戶口既錢由HSBC 過去citi <span style=\"color: teal;\">#boycottHSBC</span><br />\n2. 每月抽一個星期完全唔用八達通<br />\n3. 將50% 投資係中資股既錢轉移美股<br />\n4. 只吃非藍店，只買非藍Luxury。<span style=\"color: teal;\">#NoMoreBlue</span><br />\n5. 每月定額捐出$500 比人道基金<br />\n6. 積極尋求受影響既黃色商店，做到破壞經濟之餘，令黃店逆市回升 <span style=\"color: teal;\">#SupportYellow</span><br />\n7. 做一樣幫助香港邁向民主既事，例如：加入工會，定期討論；加入社區成為區議員義工；減少幫襯協助籠斷市場既餐廳；參加公民課堂<br />\n8. 身壯力健，全民練體能！<br />\n9. 抗爭進化，為自己定立長期目標，唔會越過底線，但唔會固步自封，謹守崗位。<br />\n10. 教育好下一代，多啲同新一代溝通，多啲影嚮中學生甚至中學生，聽下佢地諗法，keep住張民主既概念教育比下一代。<br />\n<br />\n記住係set自己既resolution之前，記住利用出名既 &quot;SMART goals&quot; 框架<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">S</span></strong>pecific (simple, sensible, significant).<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">M</span></strong>easurable (meaningful, motivating).<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">A</span></strong>chievable (agreed, attainable).<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">R</span></strong>elevant (reasonable, realistic and resourced, results-based).<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">T</span></strong>ime bound (time-based, time limited, time/cost limited, timely, time-sensitive).<br />\n<br />\n以下係啲hashtag idea 歡迎大家比下意見。<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">#NewYearsResolution<br />\n#NoMoreBlue<br />\n#NoMoreBlutatlity<br />\n#HKResolution<br />\n#Resolution4HK</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Yellow </strong>is the <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>New Sexy</strong></span></span><br />\n#FiveDemandsNotOneLess<br />\n#StandWithHongKong"},{"pid":"7cfc7ac880666cbc83f88fc79c7c7d91d5475bfc","tid":1799653,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:17:29.000Z","msg":"歡迎各位推一推身邊淺黃絲一齊進化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e8416e54d0ed4d8b66363a0a5a04bd908bce64","tid":1799653,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:18:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21b4c037da43da451954192db3e31fcdbf634f7a","tid":1799653,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:19:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afa9098ae3779005239e8319c023b5fecd07abb5","tid":1799653,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:20:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ae8d7befc45c318e3558a73c26c52468cc0fc6c","tid":1